{"tid":1437909,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根據公安條例，殯葬祭祀的集會無需事先申請。","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:56:10.000Z","uid":20137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b48c9f368c86f1c760fdab01795ed3f62214be67","tid":1437909,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"【8.9 除惡盂蘭燒衣晚會&mdash;黃大仙】<br />\n市民撒至滿地溪錢後將現溪錢清理好。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發起今天晚上在沙田、黃大仙舉起「全港超幽佈施祈褔除惡盂蘭燒衣晚會」，參加的市民可自攜祭品，到現場化寶祈福。<br />\n<br />\n今晚大量警察監視活動，有配備圓盾的便衣跟大量藍帽子，最高峰時間約有十架載有警員的衝鋒車。根據公安條例，殯葬祭祀的集會無需事先申請。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnitedSocialPress/posts/2653089368057313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnitedSocialPress%2Fposts%2F2653089368057313&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=b9926b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnitedSocialPress/posts/2653089368057313</a>"}]}